com.shopgun.android.sdk.utils

Class SgnJson

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.shopgun.android.sdk.utils.SgnJson

  • public class SgnJson
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class designed to simplify working with JSON in Android - specifically the ShopGun Android SDK. The class holds some static methods for converting data, and ensuring that valid data returns.
